EXHALING DRILL 1: 4 x any stroke 2 x fc 4 x any stroke 2 x fc
Take the rest that you feel like you need between reps.
4 x 25m of each of:- - Push off (torpedo) practice exhaling bubbles as you kick your legs. When you need to breathe, swim to the end ( any stroke) - Fc, focus on exhaling - Blowing out through your mouth whilst your face is in the water - Fc swim, focus on exhaling - Fc - 1&3 breathing every 2 to your weak side - Fc - focus on exhaling
Run easy, with breathing light. You should be able to hold a conversation through out
